          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Armed Services Always Paid Act or ASAP Act</b></p> <p>This bill provides funding to continue the pay and allowances of members of the Armed Forces, including reserve personnel, during any period of lapsed appropriations. </p>]]></text>
